title: Executive Order 6133-Authorizing the Appointment of Mrs. Elizabeth Horter
content: Mrs. Elizabeth Horter may be appointed to a classified position in the Department of State without regard to the requirements of the Civil Sendee rules.
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 6133-Authorizing the Appointment of Mrs. Elizabeth Horter Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/361960
